<figure class=\"wp-block-coblocks-gallery-offset__figure\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"518\" height=\"1000\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/35-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"2640\" data-imglink=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2640\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/35-2.jpg 518w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/35-2-155x300.jpg 155w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/35-2-78x150.jpg 78w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/35-2-500x965.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 518px) 100vw, 518px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><li class=\"coblocks-gallery--item\"><figure class=\"wp-block-coblocks-gallery-offset__figure\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"726\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/39-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"2641\" data-imglink=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2641\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/39-2.jpg 1000w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/39-2-300x218.jpg 300w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/39-2-150x109.jpg 150w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/39-2-768x558.jpg 768w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/39-2-500x363.jpg 500w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/39-2-800x581.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><li class=\"coblocks-gallery--item\"><figure class=\"wp-block-coblocks-gallery-offset__figure\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"636\" height=\"1000\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/41-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"2642\" data-imglink=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2642\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/41-2.jpg 636w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/41-2-191x300.jpg 191w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/41-2-95x150.jpg 95w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/41-2-500x786.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 636px) 100vw, 636px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Collection of base sketches.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter\">\n<figure class=\"size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"849\" height=\"1000\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/ssr-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2605\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/ssr-3.jpg 849w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/ssr-3-255x300.jpg 255w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/ssr-3-127x150.jpg 127w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/ssr-3-768x905.jpg 768w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/ssr-3-500x589.jpg 500w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/ssr-3-800x942.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 849px) 100vw, 849px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Sushant Singh Rajput, created in Illustrator, with movie posters as silhouette.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter\">\n<figure class=\"size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"625\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/taj-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2606\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/taj-3.jpg 1000w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/taj-3-300x188.jpg 300w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/taj-3-150x94.jpg 150w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/taj-3-768x480.jpg 768w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/taj-3-500x313.jpg 500w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/taj-3-800x500.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Taj Mahal and Himalayas, impressionist style.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter\">\n<figure class=\"size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"733\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/lion-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2604\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/lion-3.jpg 1000w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/lion-3-300x220.jpg 300w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/lion-3-150x110.jpg 150w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/lion-3-768x563.jpg 768w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/lion-3-500x367.jpg 500w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/lion-3-800x586.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Mother lion and her cub, Illustrator, with night sky as filler layer.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>For digital arts, I start on paper. Making rough or taking a finished sketch. Scan them into computer. Open scans in Photoshop. Begin adding layers. Add effects to sketches. Experiment with backgrounds, foregrounds. Place objects in scenes. Add artifacts and surroundings. Create environments around sketches. Adjust lighting, shadows, glare, reflections. Spend time colorizing sketches. Correct<a class=\"more-link\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/?page_id=1185\">Continue reading <span class=\"screen-reader-text\">&#8220;Digital Art&#8221;<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":198642521,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_coblocks_attr":"","_coblocks_dimensions":"","_coblocks_responsive_height":"","_coblocks_accordion_ie_support":"","footnotes":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1185"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/users\/198642521"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fcomments&post=1185"}],"version-history":[{"count":114,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1185\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3055,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/in